Improved Grab					KEY:Animated Rug of Welcome ~ Improved Grab	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Extraordinary.Race Trait.Animated Rug of Welcome Race Trait.SpecialQuality						DESC:To use this ability, a rug of welcome must hit a creature of its size category or smaller with its grab attack. (The rug has a +4 racial bonus on its grab attacks, already figured into the statistics above.) It can then attempt to start a grapple as a free action without provoking attacks of opportunity. If it wins the grapple check, it establishes a hold.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																														SOURCEPAGE:p.150

#Elemental Grue Common
Spell Disruption					KEY:Elemental Grue ~ Spell Disruption		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Supernatural.Race Trait.ElementalGrue Race Trait.SpecialQuality								DESC:The very presence of an elemental grue interferes with spells that affect the grue's associated element. Any spellcaster within 40 feet of a chaggrin who casts a spell with the same descriptor as the grue's element (earth, fire, air, or water) must succeed on a DC 15 caster level check or have the spell fail. Within the same area of any such spell currently in effect, a grue has a chance to dispel the effect as a free action, as if casting a targeted dispel magic (caster level 10th).																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																								SOURCEPAGE:p.153

