# Harginn
Fire Spray						KEY:Harginn ~ Fire Spray				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpellLike.Race Trait.Harginn Race Trait.SpecialQuality										DESC:As a standard action, a fire grue can create a 30-foot cone of fire, dealing 2d6 points of fire damage (Reflex DC 11 half). This ability is the equivalent of a 2nd-level spell.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																												SOURCEPAGE:p.155
Blur							KEY:Harginn ~ Blur					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpellLike.Race Trait.Harginn Race Trait.SpecialQuality										DESC:Fire grues naturally flicker and waver continuously as if under the effect of a blur spell (caster level 10th). They have concealment against all attacks by creatures that rely on sight.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																											SOURCEPAGE:p.155

