Invisible						KEY:Ildriss ~ Invisible					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Supernatural.Race Trait.Ildriss Race Trait.SpecialQuality									DESC:Air grues are naturally invisible, gaining total concealment.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.155

